THAT'S A PERSON WHO'S
NEVER BEEN MARRIED.

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:25.000
(Marc) THERE'S MORE - THERE'S
MORE OF A STABILITY RIGHT NOW

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:28.000
THAN THERE WAS OVER THE
LAST TWO YEARS, I GUESS.

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:31.000
AND SO I DECIDED, "WELL THE
KID SHOULD HAVE HER OWN ROOM".

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:34.000
AND SO, AT THIS POINT
IN TIME, WE'RE RENTING.

