THE BATHROOM. AND SO I HAD TO
GATHER EVERYTHING OUT AND PUT IT

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:06.000
IN A LITTLE BOX UNTIL THE
PLUMBER CAME IN TO REPAIR,

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:10.000
CORRECT WHATEVER, WHATEVER THE
PROBLEM WAS. SO SHE COMES HOME

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:12.000
FROM SCHOOL, COMES UPSTAIRS AND
GOES, "OH MY GOD, DADDY,

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:14.000
ARE WE MOVING AGAIN?!"
