AND AS SHE GETS MORE MATURE,
THAT'LL ONLY GET BETTER.

00:13:44.000 --> 00:13:48.000
UNTIL OF COURSE, SHE HAS HER
FIRST PERIOD, AND GETS INTO

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:51.000
PUBERTY AND THEN SHE'LL
TELL ME THAT I'M AN IDIOT.

00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:55.000
REEL THIS IN AND LET'S
SEE IF THERE'S FISH AT
THE END OF IT.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:57.000
SO I GUESS I'VE GOT SOMETHING
TO LOOK FORWARD TO.

